♪ Never going home again ♪

28:04.560 --> 28:06.937
- Ay, Pilar.

28:11.942 --> 28:16.947
♪ Never going home again ♪

28:17.531 --> 28:18.949
What the...

28:21.660 --> 28:24.663
♪ Falling in, inch by inch ♪

28:25.163 --> 28:27.165
♪ I'm not resisting ♪

28:27.749 --> 28:33.297
♪ And I'm... addicted tonight ♪

28:33.297 --> 28:35.883
